348
00:27:29,020 --> 00:27:30,020
 Pa daj, budite drugačiji.

349
00:27:30,020 --> 00:27:31,020
 Kaži, ja neću tako.

350
00:27:31,020 --> 00:27:32,520
 Ja hoću biti drugačiji.

351
00:27:32,520 --> 00:27:35,600
 Ja sam stavno nedavno jednog, ja on im priča, ima 15 dana,

352
00:27:35,600 --> 00:27:37,980
 imam dečka u Zagrebu, u 17. godina.

353
00:27:37,980 --> 00:27:40,380
 Ja sam imao misu, prije mise, on mene moli,

354
00:27:40,380 --> 00:27:43,560
